  "_comment": "Craftiloo Master Skill Scheduler — complete new architecture (2026-03-13). ALL executions use skill-api HTTP (port 5680) — no executeCommand nodes (n8n is Docker, no host shell access). Monday pipeline calls sub-workflow yUafv7HE3fSAgliu. Tuesday and Friday autonomous sessions are inline. Weekly schedule: Mon data pipeline → Tue agent deep-dive → Fri agent validation.",
